       <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://blogs.westmont.edu/2015/01/29/talk-probes-christian-efforts-to-end-slavery/" rel="bookmark">Talk Probes Christian Efforts to End Slavery</a></h2> 
       <div class="post-info">
        <span class="date published time" title="2015-01-29T12:04:44+00:00">January 29, 2015</span> 
       </div>
       <div class="entry-content"> 
