         <a href="http://blogs.westmont.edu/2015/01/23/kearns-goodwin-to-speak-at-breakfast/"><img width="168" height="168" src="http://blogs.westmont.edu/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Goodwin_DorisKearns_ORIGINAL-168x168-1422060850.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Doris Kearns Goodwin"></a>
        </div> 
