        </div> 
        <p>Golfers and disc golfers will have a unique opportunity to play together in the seventh annual Will’s Tourney on Monday, Feb. 2, at 11:30 a.m. at the Glen Annie Golf Club. A buffet dinner, raffle and awards presentation will follow the tournament at 5:15 p.m. All proceeds from the event benefit the William Wiersma Endowment… [<a class="read-more" href="http://blogs.westmont.edu/2015/01/13/stick-disc-golfers-take-aim-at-tourney/">Continue Reading</a>]</p> 
